{
  "text": "Assume for the moment that D is of finite type and let n = |S|. Then W D can be realized as a group of orthogonal transformations of R n with generators x equal to reflections [CITATION_1] . Let A be the set of hyperplanes coresponding to all the reflections in W D . For any point e in R n \\ A we denote by P D the convex hull of the orbit of e under the action of W D . The face lattice of the n-dimensional convex polytope P D depends only on the graph D",
